        "subject": "LU-00000 build: Insist on ko tests",
        "message": "LU-00000 build: Insist on ko tests\n\nCurrently the build tests only demand an object (.o) be\ncreated from a compile test.\n\nHowever in the case of a missing symbol exports a (.o) will\nbe generated and a kernel module (.ko) will not created.\n\nDefault to stricter enforcement.\n\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I5881bff3be1eff638afdb16a6d0929379af67e32\n"
